name: Volatile stability
description: In the uncontrolled chaos comes form- When creating something new there is a process of excitement that can tangent all over, connecting ideas in unpredictable ways. It can be equal parts stimulating and draining. Much like the process of creating a block on the chain, prior to their completion blocks may look very random and erratic in movement. Sooner or later though, the block is on the ledger forever â€“ a digital obelisk to eternally represent the efforts we all put in to create community.
